{
  "texts": [
    "However, costs and limitations in access were seen as obstacles.",
    "One participant stated, \"New technologies, especially the newest technologies, are very costly in the first place.",
    "For this reason, I can't reach them easily in my private life or school education (P.12).",
    "\"The contribution of artificial intelligence in the health field was generally considered positive.",
    "The most critical concern in this regard was the changes it would bring in professional practices and the decreased need for labor in some areas."
  ]
}